---
import Icon from "heroicons-astro/HeroIcon.astro";
---
<h1 id="about-heading" class="relative bottom-4 right-2 sm:right-0 multi-col:right-16 text-7xl sm:text-8xl multi-col:text-10xl wide:text-11xl uppercase outlined text-transparent">About</h1>

<div class="flex flex-row bg-off-white-transparent backdrop-blur-md rounded-md shadow-md p-6 w-full my-6 multi-col:my-12">
  <p class="text-off-black">
    As an engineering student who originally embarked on a journey in Mechanical Engineering, I unexpectedly discovered my true passion for coding during my undergraduate studies. This newfound interest led me to enroll in a full-stack web development bootcamp, all while juggling the responsibilities of a full-time job, to fully immerse myself in the world of software development. 
    <br/> 
    <br/>
    Today, I'm excited to welcome you to my online studio, a platform where I aim to tackle the challenges faced by our community through innovative software solutions. Each project featured here is a testament to my journey and dedication to creating impactful software, one piece at a time.
    <br/> 
    <br/>
    <span class="font-bold">
      - Josh Stubbington
    </span>
  </p>
</div>

