            <div>
              <div class="text-sm">
                <a href="#" class="font-medium text-gray-900">Launched Twin Spruce Studios</a>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-off-black-transparent-dark">Q1 2024</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <p>Twin Spruce Studios is named after the cherished childhood home where I grew up, flanked by two majestic spruce trees that stood as silent witnesses to countless dreams and adventures. This studio embodies the spirit of innovation and resilience instilled in me from those early days, dedicated to crafting software solutions that bring positive change.</p>
